<br>
This was introduced as part of the Tynnonium Shackle.  Simply walk up to Glox and say &quot;I am ready&quot;<br>
<br>
You'll port to a small room in the Shaman guild.  Use ID to fear the Glox mob here (don't worry he's not a level 61 GM) out of the locked room.  He will then summon you out.  Whack him down and get yourself a free port potion.<br>
<br>
One major downside.  This potion is NO RENT.  So you'll need to do this at the beginning of your fear session. <p>Tarrask, 49th Swifttail of Saryrn
