<br>
Another potion shamans can make are Stinging Wort.  Warning:  these are very costly, but could save you in a near death situation.  I carry a 10 dose on me (even though my partner is a shaman, I still had to dish out the pp for it, but feel safer <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) that will heal 250hp's.  Won't be able to cast while feigned (recently discovered) but it's an instant cast and can be used once you stand up.<br>
